divs: sighting detailsbright flare like object traveling east to west in vicinity of rte 108\rte 33 in stratham nh. low in sky (maybe 1000 ft) witnessed over a distance of maybe 2 miles before object appeared to burn-out. we were traveling at aprox 50 mph, object estimated at aprox 100 mph+. i've never seen a green flare that could travel such a distance, but that is what it looked like.
Summary: Bright shooting green light low in sky
